{"type":null,"faqId":9353,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00）如何关闭和启用数据业务","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>关闭和开启数据业务的方法：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入系统设置主菜单，选择<b>全部设置</b></span><span><span> &gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">移动网络</span><span><span> &gt; </span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">数据连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选“中国移动”（或“中国联通”，表示卡的信息），打开数据连接，勾选关闭，表示关闭数据业务。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>在下拉通知栏中打开数据开关。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">进入系统设置主菜单，选择<b>全部设置</b></span><span><b> </b><span>&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">双卡设置</span><span> </span></b><span><span>&gt; </span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">数据连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选“中国移动”（或“中国联通”，表示卡的信息），打开数据连接，勾选关闭，表示关闭数据业务。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:8pt;font-family:Wingdings;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">为了您能够尽量的享受高速数据业务，手机将会自动将</span><span><span>3G</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">服务也切换到您开启数据业务的卡槽上。比如你插入了两张卡，一张中国移动一张中国联通的</span><span><span>SIM</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡，如果你在设置里开启当前使用联通卡进行数据业务，那么联通卡槽就会自动切换到</span><span><span>3G</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络，移动卡槽就会自动是</span><span><span>2G</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">网络，不需要用户手动设置。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从屏幕下拉通知栏，点击数据开关<img height=\"36\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29813\" width=\"31\" /></span><span><span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，可以打开数据业务，打开后状态为高亮</span><span><span> <img style=\"width:36px;height:36px;\" height=\"45\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29814\" width=\"36\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9950","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396240370000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":132,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"上网","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}